s: submitting written request and lump-sum payment, lender applying funds to principal, recalculating your payment, updating systems, and implementing new payment amount. Your new lower payment typically begins the following month after completion. This is dramatically faster than refinancing's typical one to two month timeline requiring full underwriting and closing process."}}]};
